name: Old and New - Two American Airlines 777-200ERs Landing at LAX ᴴᴰ
description:
Hey everyone, here`s another LAX video shot from Imperial Hill, featuring two American Airlines 777s landing one after the other on Runway 25L. Unfortunately, the touchdowns were blocked by a parked Kalitta Air 747-200 that apparently never moves. 

Anyone that is affected by the crash of Malaysia Airlines flight 370 has my complete sympathy. R.I.P. to all those that perished.

Thanks for watching. Please comment, rate, and subscribe.
